[b]Description:[/b] 
the Program allows the user to create a family tree and display it in several ways. 
Tools used when working with family tree: the insertion of data for each member of the family, the insertion of data on families,
 virtual tree, family assistant, chart of descendants and ancestors, fan chart, timeline, virtual globe, family chart, that, media reports about the persons in the tree. 
The program allows you to import data in GEDCOM format with UTF or ANSI. 
The program allows you to export data to the HTML standard
